    "causal_summary": "The shared/runtime part of system-spec-kit contains an underscore-bearing shared/mcp_server directory even though its TypeScript/shared-package surface can use kebab-case. This phase verifies the runtime tree, renames the permitted shared directory, updates its references, and preserves package manifests, tool names, generated databases, and Python package directories.",
